## Stage 9: Namespaces & Resource Organization (Week 7)

```bash
kubectl create namespace staging
kubectl get pods -n staging
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml -n staging
kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=staging   # switch default namespace
```

Use namespaces to separate environments (`dev`, `staging`, `prod`) or teams within one cluster.

